00:08:56.133 --> 00:08:57.830 align:middle line:90%
what you want to explore.

00:08:57.830 --> 00:08:59.260 align:middle line:84%
I look at this
planet as if it was

00:08:59.260 --> 00:09:02.688 align:middle line:84%
a three-dimensional amusement
park where total immersion

00:09:02.688 --> 00:09:05.230 align:middle line:84%
movies are filmed, and you can
play with any inner experience

00:09:05.230 --> 00:09:06.030 align:middle line:90%
you want.

00:09:06.030 --> 00:09:07.880 align:middle line:84%
>> But the total
immersion, we're in it.

00:09:07.880 --> 00:09:09.860 align:middle line:84%
We're right in the
middle of all of this.

00:09:09.860 --> 00:09:10.660 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:09:10.660 --> 00:09:13.450 align:middle line:84%
What if people are feeling
