00:09:49.090 --> 00:09:51.490 align:middle line:84%
the books that are written,
the stories that rivet us

00:09:51.490 --> 00:09:53.170 align:middle line:84%
when we're reading
the newspaper,

00:09:53.170 --> 00:09:55.060 align:middle line:84%
