by everything.

00:09:55.060 --> 00:09:56.810 align:middle line:84%
The so-called good and
bad, dark and evil.

00:09:56.810 --> 00:09:58.018 align:middle line:90%
We're interested [INAUDIBLE].

00:09:58.018 --> 00:10:00.670 align:middle line:84%
Some people are more interested
in really deeply exploring it

00:10:00.670 --> 00:10:02.643 align:middle line:84%
at a very deeper
level than others.

00:10:02.643 --> 00:10:04.060 align:middle line:84%
But the question
that you asked, I

00:10:04.060 --> 00:10:05.477 align:middle line:84%
