So it's OK--

00:10:52.950 --> 00:10:53.750 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:10:53.750 --> 00:10:54.990 align:middle line:90%
>> --whatever we are doing.

00:10:54.990 --> 00:10:55.130 align:middle line:90%
Oh.

00:10:55.130 --> 00:10:55.930 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:10:55.930 --> 00:10:58.780 align:middle line:84%
>> You're just fine, exactly,
with what's going on.

00:10:58.780 --> 00:11:00.520 align:middle line:84%
I came to a lot of
the realizations that

00:11:00.520 --> 00:11:03.460 align:middle line:84%
are in the book
