00:11:12.190 --> 00:11:13.180 align:middle line:90%
Everything fell apart.

00:11:13.180 --> 00:11:15.260 align:middle line:84%
And I was like,
I'm the same guy.

00:11:15.260 --> 00:11:16.690 align:middle line:84%
I'm making decisions
the same way.

00:11:16.690 --> 00:11:18.910 align:middle line:84%
Why am I getting this
dramatically different result,

00:11:18.910 --> 00:11:20.910 align:middle line:84%
and everything I touch
