00:11:24.820 --> 00:11:26.800 align:middle line:90%
and I wanted to change things.

00:11:26.800 --> 00:11:29.860 align:middle line:84%
But now I look back, and I see
that each one of those scenes

00:11:29.860 --> 00:11:32.320 align:middle line:84%
was perfectly orchestrated
to get me to a place

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:33.820 align:middle line:90%
now that I'm really happy with.

00:11:33.820 --> 00:11:36.070 align:middle line:84%
